"height":1040,"file_path":"/rwUYnmT1mJQ7jBCrZpJd0i4uSLZ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0},{"width":1850,"height":1040,"file_path":"/tkxgPhxpH1DMxDrhQRICYnmfe0Y.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0},{"width":1850,"height":1040,"file_path":"/oi26oZU0dYfGGrgwqZBopMbz86G.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0},{"width":2560,"height":1440,"file_path":"/sH7p9ejux1SgXaxAlyPNXkPdHIu.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2586,"height":1454,"file_path":"/hFKB4UF9BBiWJSzrr2UZYUBwc7x.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0},{"width":2560,"height":1440,"file_path":"/AuLYwbp3E0ODDfThMUqNj32kkEr.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/AclC4dOr9w7JNwNmGUmYVVtIytP.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:58:50.526+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":93,"tagline":"Can a pig really fly?","homepage":"","overview":"In Italy in the 1930s, sky pirates in biplanes terrorize wealthy cruise ships as they sail the Adriatic Sea. The only pilot brave enough to stop the scourge is the mysterious Porco Rosso, a former World War I flying ace who was somehow turned into a pig during the war. As he prepares to battle the pirate crew's American ace, Porco Rosso enlists the help of spunky girl mechanic Fio Piccolo and his longtime friend Madame Gina."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.universumfilm.de/filme/136081/porco-rosso.html","overview":"Porco Rosso, ein Mensch mit Schweinegesicht, ist ein Fliegerass. Statt für die italienische Luftwaffe zu fliegen, verdient der coole, einsame Macho sein Geld lieber als Kopfgeldjäger und jagt Luftpiraten ihre Beute ab, denn \"Ich bin lieber ein Schwein als ein Faschist\". Für ein Duell mit einem amerikanischen Flieger muss er sein rotes Flugzeug generalüberholen lassen - ausgerechnet unter der Leitung einer vorwitzigen 17-Jährigen, die natürlich auch noch mitfliegen will. Die Luftpiraten richten das große Duell aus."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"I sine unge dage var Porco Rosso den mest frygtede kamppilot under 1. Verdenskrig. Men efter at hele hans deling blev dræbt, forvandledes den smukke unge mand på mærkværdig vis, og fik et ansigt som en lyserød gris. Flere år senere er han flyttet ud på en øde ø, men så snart telefonen ringer, går han i luften for at jage de pirater, der hærger turistskibene ud for Italiens kyst. Porco Rosso er også lidt af en “cool cat”. Han slår sig løs i nattelivet, drikker whisky, og slipper helst ikke sit elskede cigaretrør. Men en dag indhenter fortiden ham, og ikke mindst hans store kærlighed..."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":93,"tagline":"Un cerdo tiene que volar","homepage":"","overview":"Periodo de entreguerras. Porco es un cerdo aviador que fustra todos los actos de piratería perpetrados por los piratas aéreos del Adriático. Éstos, decididos a acabar con el valiente y hábil Porco, se unen para contratar a un aventurero americano que le elimine de los aires donde las mafias operan"},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"Un maiale che è riuscito a volare.","homepage":"","overview":"In quella che Miyazaki Hayao definisce “l’epoca degli idrovolanti”, Marco Pagot è un ex-pilota che si è misteriosamente ritrovato nelle mutate sembianze di un maiale antropomorfo. Con il nome di battaglia di Porco Rosso, vola alla ventura sui cieli dell’Adriatico a bordo del suo idrovolante vermiglio, sfuggendo al giogo fascista e sbarcando il lunario come cacciatore di taglie. Ma l’arrivo del pilota americano Curtis, assoldato dai Pirati del Cielo, lo costringerà a nuove battaglie per salvare il proprio onore e quello di una radiosa fanciulla, per la riconquista di un perduto amore e della fiducia nell’umanità."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":93,"tagline":"Un pilote de légende !","homepage":"","overview":"Dans l'entre-deux-guerres quelque part en Italie, le pilote Marco, aventurier solitaire, vit dans le repaire qu'il a établi sur une île déserte de l'Adriatique. À bord de son splendide hydravion rouge, il vient en aide aux personnes en difficulté."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso - O Porquinho Voador","runtime":94,"tagline":"Um porco tem de voar.","homepage":"","overview":"A Primeira Guerra Mundial acabou. Muitos aviadores viraram-se para a pirataria aérea, na qual emerge um herói; Porco Rosso, um homem com uma cabeça de porco, antes conhecido por Marco Pagot. Quando é desafiado por Curtis, um americano que voa com os piratas, Porco Rosso é forçado a defender a sua honra contra o recém-chegado, o que o leva até a Fio Piccolo, uma jovem engenheira cheia de vida que reconstrói o avião de Porco para o grande combate."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://triart.se/filmer/porco-rosso/","overview":"Mästerpiloten Porco Rosso har genom en förbannelse förvandlats till en gris. När han utmanas av den hetlevrade amerikanen Curtis måste han, med hjälp av den unge Fio, få sitt något slitna plan tillbaka i dugligt skick. Samtidigt försöker Porco Rosso vinna tillbaka sin älskades hjärta."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"红猪","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1930年代的意大利，一位第一次世界大战的王牌飞行员因诅咒变成了猪面人。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":93,"tagline":"カッコイイとは、こういうことさ。","homepage":"https://www.ghibli.jp/works/porco/","overview":"飛行艇を操る空賊が横行していた、第一次大戦後のイタリアはアドリア海。賞金稼ぎの飛行艇乗りであるポルコ・ロッソは、空賊たちには天敵の存在。自分の顔を魔法で豚に変えてしまったポルコを何とかやっつけたいと一計を案じた空賊たちは、アメリカからスゴ腕の飛行艇乗りを呼び寄せ、彼に一騎打ちを迫る。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Het is 1930. Het is de tijd van lucht-piraten, premiejagers en allerlei ander soort piloten. De sluwste en beste van alle piloten is Porco Rosso. Porco Rosso is een man met het hoofd van een varken. Hij verdient zijn brood door middel van baantjes zoals mensen redden van piraten."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Szkarłatny pilot","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Włochy, lata 30. ubiegłego wieku. Za sterami czerwonego samolotu siedzi mężczyzna z głową świni. To słynny as przestworzy, znany jako Porco Rosso czyli Szkarłatny Pirat. Doskonały pilot i otoczony powszechnym szacunkiem bohater, który niezwykle skutecznie zwalcza powietrznych piratów rabujących i porywających ludzi dla okupu. Ci jednak nie pozostają bezczynni. Wynajmują równie utalentowanego pilota, Amerykanina Donalda Curtisa, aby zlikwidował problem, jakim jest Szkarłatny Pilot. Bezlitosny Curtis nie cofnie się przed niczym, żeby wygrać z naszym bohaterem nie tylko pojedynek w przestworzach, ale też rywalizację o względy pewnej pięknej kobiety…"},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Порко Россо","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Марко Пагот, отважный пилот и герой Первой мировой войны, потерял веру в человечество. Это стало проклятием, которое превратило его в человекообразную свинью, и теперь Марко известен как Порко Россо. Порко занялся охотой на воздушных пиратов, грабящих суда и яхты, но однажды ему самому предстоит стать мишенью. Сможет ли он избежать преследования и вернуть человеческий облик?"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Punainen sika","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Porco Rosson tarina sijoittuu 20-luvun lopun Italiaan, jossa ensimmäisen maailmansodan lentäjistä on tullut maattomia seikkailijoita - Välimeren villejä viikinkejä ja hurjia ryöväreitä. Adrianmeren uljaista lentäjä-ässistä legendaarisin on Porco Rosso. Lentäjällä on sian ulkomuoto, mutta hänen rinnassaan sykkii sankarin lämmin sydän. Ja aivan erityisesti se sykkii Välimeren viehkeimmälle kaunottarelle."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"붉은 돼지","runtime":90,"tagline":"낭만을 꿈꾸는 로맨티스트","homepage":"","overview":"제1차 세계대전이 끝난 후, 전쟁의 기억을 지우기 위해 스스로 돼지로 변한 이탈리아 공군의 에이스 비행사 포르코 롯소. 그는 이탈리아 근해의 무인도에서 혼자 지내며 그의 의지대로 자유롭게 날고 하늘의 해적을 소탕한다. 젊은 시절 인간의 모습을 한 얼굴은 지나의 레스토랑의 벽에 걸려 있는 사진 속에 유일하게 남아 있다. 사람들로부터 붉은 돼지로 불리는 포르코 롯소는 미국인 조종사 도널드 커티스의 공격으로 비행기가 파손되자, 비행기 제작자인 피콜로에게 수리를 요청한다. 피콜로의 손녀인 피오는 포르코 롯소와 함께 지내며 온갖 모험을 겪으면서 조금씩 그를 좋아하게 되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso - A mesterpilóta","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Az első világháború után az Adria felett nyüzsögtek a légikalózok, akik a védtelen utasszállító hajókat fosztogatták. A kalózok hírhedt ellensége Porco Rosso, aki valaha ember volt: az olasz légierő kitűnő pilótája. Egy légicsata egyedüli túlélőjeként végignézte társai tragikus"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Porco Rosso er en fantasifull historie om en italiensk flyverhelt fra første verdenskrig som etter krigen lever som dusørjeger i kamp mot «luftpirater» i Adriaterhavet. Helten, som er blitt omskapt slik at han har grisehode, het tidligere Marco Pagot, men kalles nå bare Porco Rosso, det vil si «rød gris» på italiensk. Filmen er fritt basert på Miyazakis manga-tegneserie Hikōtei Jidai og inneholder en blanding av eventyr og realisme med morsomme figurer, lange flysekvenser, barnslig komikk og voksne referanser."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"חזיר באוויר","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"טייס הרפתקן באיטליה של שנות ה-30, צופה בנשמתם של טייסים בעודם נמשכים לגן עדן ונענש בכך שראשו מוחלף בראש של חזיר. עכשיו הוא יוצא למסע הצלה של טייסים בידי שודדי אוויר אוויליים ונלחם בנמסיס שלו, דונלד קרטיס, שמתחרה אתו גם בעניין השמלות. סרטו של אחד מבמאי האנימציה החשובים בעולם, הייאו מייאזקי, שנים מספר לפני ההצלחה הפנומנלית של \"המסע המופלא\" ו-\"הטירה הנעה של האול\"."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"紅豬","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"故事由一個由於魔法而變成豬的飛行員，「波魯克・羅素」，追擊「曼馬由特空中海賊團」（簡稱曼馬由特隊）開始。曼馬由特隊打劫了一艘由威尼斯出發的郵輪，並且綁架了小學女校的學生，波魯克成功的打敗了曼馬由特隊，也結下了樑子。  於是曼馬由特隊等的空中海賊團聯盟（簡稱空賊聯盟），請來了美國的飛行好手「卡地士」來當空賊聯盟的保鏢，除了協助空賊聯盟的行動，更在波魯克前往米蘭要保養飛行艇的途中，趁波魯克的引擎故障，將波魯克的飛行艇擊落使其必須進行大修。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Кнур Багряний","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Італія. Післявоєнні часи. У країні владу захоплює Муссоліні й починає встановлювати фашистську диктатуру. Марко Паґот, більш відомий як Порко Росо, після першої світової війни розчарувався у війні й почав вести тихе відлюдне життя, перебиваючись винагородою за порятунок кораблів від піратів. І тут його розмірене життя перериває американський пілот Катіс, що вирішив помірятись із ним силами."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Kırmızı Kanatlar","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1920'lerin Adriyatik Denizi'nde sadece bir tek pilot göklerin hakimidir: Porco Rosso, büyülü güçler tarafından domuza çevirilmiş yetenekli pilot. Porco, uçakları gökyüzündeki diğer çete uçaklarından koruduğu yalnız bir hayat sürmektedir. Hayatını kendine ait bir adada yaşayarak ve otel sahibi güzel arkadaşı Gina'yı ziyaret ederek geçirmektedir. Ancak bir gün Porco'yu ve uçağını vurarak kendi ününü yaratmak isteyen bir pilot adaya gelir. Bunun üzerine Porco genç mühendis arkadaşından uçağını bu büyük savaşa hazır hale getirmesini ister..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso: O Último Herói Romântico","runtime":93,"tagline":"Um porco tem que voar.","homepage":"https://studioghibli.com.br/filmografia/porco-rosso/","overview":"Na Itália, durante o período entre as duas guerras, com um fundo de recessão económica e de ascensão do fascismo, perdido numa ilha deserta no mar Adriático, um ex-piloto emérito da Força Aérea Italiana, se vê transformado em um porco e converte-se em caçador de recompensas. Ele se chama \"Porco Rosso\". A bordo de seu hidroavião vermelho, ele tem muitas aventuras: de caça aos piratas do ar que fizeram um hábito de roubar os turistas que visitam a região, o resgate de passageiros tomados como reféns, duelos aéreos, \"corridas\" de hidroavião, subterfúgios para semear a polícia secreta italiana... a vida do piloto é agitada e cheia de aventuras."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"پورکو روسو","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"در طول آغاز سال‌های رکود بزرگ، زندگی در دریای مدیترانه و سواحل اطراف آن بسیار دشوار شده بود. غارت و تاخت و تاز دزدان هوایی بسیار زیاد شده، بنابراین به وجود محافظان ماهر نیاز است. یک از بهترین محافظان یک خوک بنام «پورکو روسو» است که زمانی انسان و یک خلبان درجه یک در زمان جنگ جهانی اول بوده است او حالا به کسانی که دچار تنگدستی شده‌اند بدون هیچ گونه چشمداشتی کمک می‌کند..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"飛天紅豬俠","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"第一次大戰剛結束時，一群傑出機師因生活所迫淪為海盜，在亞德里亞海橫行無忌。重償之下，飛天紅豬俠阿 LAM 挺身而出，將海盜打得潰不成軍。為了清除眼中釘，海盜從美國請來了奸狡的外援阿福。兩雄相遇的一刻，阿福卻被飛天紅豬俠的紅顏知己卿卿所迷倒，兩人繼而為了金錢、榮譽和心儀的卿卿、豆釘，展開了一場扣人心絃的生死空中大決戰……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Порко Росо","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Οι Αερομαχίες του Πόρκο Ρόσο","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ένα γουρούνι πρέπει να πετάξει.","homepage":"","overview":"Όταν αεροπειρατές τρομοκρατούν την Αδριατική Θάλασσα, μόνο αυτός ο Ιταλός πιλότος δεν φοβάται να τα βάλει μαζί τους. Το πρόβλημα; Είναι μισός άνθρωπος μισός γουρούνι."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"بوركو روسو","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تدور أحداث القصة حول \"بوركو روسو\" أو الخنزير القرمزي، و هو طيار ماهر في فترة بداية صعود الفاشية في إيطاليا مسخ خنزيرا بعد أن عاد من الموت في الحرب. بين كبريائه كطيار و كرهه للقتل و الحرب و للفاشية و حبه المكبوت للمغنية جينا تدور أحداث الفيلم."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Japonský film Kurenai no Buta se odehrává ve třicátých letech dvacátého století v prosluněné Itálii. Pojednává o odvážném pilotovi Porco Rossovi, kterému se stala zvláštní věc... Při jedné letecké bitvě, kdy už zraněný a vyčerpaný Porco nemohl pokračovat, se najednou ocitl nad mraky. Motor měl vypnutý, ale přesto stál na místě. A pak se to stalo. Zpoza mraků začaly vylétávat všichni, kteří se té bitvy zúčastnili, všichni Porcovi kamarádi, a začali vzlétat k nebi. Všichni, kromě Porca. Ten jediný zůstal, a od té doby má prasečí obličej. Kletba však není jediná věc se kterou se musí vypořádat. Nad Jadranským mořem se objevil nový pilot, Američan Donald Curtis, který chce být za každou cenu nejlepší a chce se s Porcem utkat v leteckém souboji. A nechce se bít jen o čest, ale i o lásku místní majitelky hotelu, a Porcovu lásku z dětství Giny. Podaří se Porcovi zlomit kletbu? Podaří se mu získat zpět svou dávnou lásku?"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":93,"tagline":"Un cerdo tiene que volar.","homepage":"","overview":"Periodo de entreguerras. Porco es un cerdo aviador que frustra todos los actos de piratería perpetrados por los piratas aéreos del Adriático. Éstos, decididos a acabar con el valiente y hábil aviador, se ponen de acuerdo para contratar a un aventurero americano cuya misión será eliminarlo."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"พอร์โค รอสโซ สลัดอากาศประจัญบาน","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เมื่อสลัดอากาศเข้ารุกรานน่านฟ้าเหนือทะเลเอเดรียติก นักบินอิตาลีคนนี้เท่านั้นที่กล้าพอจะต่อกรกับเหล่าร้าย แต่ว่าเขาเป็นครึ่งคนครึ่่งหมูนะ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Taliansko, 30. roky 20. storočia. Príbeh pojednáva o odvážnom pilotovi Porco Rossovi, ktorému sa stala zvláštna vec. Pri jednej leteckej bitke, kedy už zranený a vyčerpaný nemohol pokračovať, sa zrazu ocitol nad oblakmi. Motor mal vypnutý, ale napriek tomu stál na mieste. A potom sa to stalo. Spoza mrakov začali vylietavať všetci, ktorí sa tej bitky zúčastnili, všetci Porcoví kamaráti, a začali vzlietať k nebu. Všetci, okrem Porca. Ten jediný zostal, a od tej doby má prasaciu tvár. Kliatba však nie je jediná vec s ktorou sa musí vysporiadať. Nad Jadranským morom sa objavil nový pilot, Američan Donald Curtis, ktorý chce byť za každú cenu najlepší a chce sa s Porcom stretnúť v leteckom súboji. A nechce sa biť len o česť, ale aj o lásku miestnej majiteľky hotela, a Porcovu lásku z detstva Giny. Podarí sa Porcovi zlomiť kliatbu? Podarí sa mu získať späť svoju dávnu lásku?"},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gerra arteko denboran, Benito Mussolini Italian diktadore da. Marco Pagot piloto militar italiar aritua da, lagun bat gudan hiltzen ikusi ondoren, sorginkeri berezi baten biktima bihurtzen da, txerri itxura ematen diona. Honen ondorioz baita bere hidrohegazkina gorria dela eta, \"Porco Rosso\" ezizena hartzen du eta ordainsari ehiztari famatua bilakatzen da, Adriatiko itsasoan piraten lapurretak ezeztatzen dituena. Piratek, Porcotaz nazkaturik kontraerasotzea erabakitzen dute estatubatuar abenturazale bat kontratatzen."},"name":"euskera","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Basque"},{"data":{"title":"Chú Heo Màu Đỏ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Không tặc hoành hành khắp vùng biển Adriatic và chỉ có tay phi công người Ý này mới đủ can trường để đương đầu với chúng. Có điều, ông ta là phi công nửa người nửa heo."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Porco rosso","runtime":0,"tagline":"El porc volador","homepage":"","overview":"A Itàlia, a la dècada de 1930, els pirates del cel en biplans aterroritzen els vaixells dels rics mentre naveguen pel mar Adriàtic. L’únic pilot prou valent com per aturar-los és el misteriós Porco Rosso, un crac volador de la Primera Guerra Mundial que d’alguna manera va ser convertit en un porc durant la guerra. Mentre es prepara per combatre l’as nord-americà de la tripulació pirata, Porco Rosso demana ajuda al mecànic de la noia Funky Piccolo i a la seva amiga de sempre Madame Gina."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pirații aerului terorizează Marea Adriatică, iar acest pilot italian este singurul suficient de curajos să îi înfrunte. O singură problemă: e jumătate om, jumătate porc."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Porco Rosso","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dans l'entre-deux-guerres quelque part en Italie, le pilote Marco, aventurier solitaire, vit dans le repaire qu'il a établi sur une île déserte de l'Adriatique. À bord de son splendide hydravion rouge, il vient en aide aux personnes en difficulté."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"პორკო როსო","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"დიდი დეპრესიის პირველ წლებში სიტუაცია ხმელთაშუა ზღვაზე ძალზედ გართულდა. მეკობრეთა დაუმთავრებელი თავდასხმების გამო ყველა იძულებული გახდა მცველი ყოლოდა. ამ საქმეში ერთ-ერთ საუკეთესოდ ითვლებოდა პორკო როსო."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Vapper siga Porco Rosso","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Elas ja oli kord lendur, tõeline õhuäss, sündinud piloot. Kui Esimene Maailmasõda lõppes, asus ta elama Aadria mere saarele ning hakkas valvama laevu piraatide eest, vabal ajalaga peesitas päikese käes ja elas oma lõbuks. Kunagi oli Marko inimene ja keegi ei tea, kuidas temast siga sai, kuid kõik teavad, et Porco Rosso on suurepärane mees, üllas ja julge, ta ei karda piraate ega fašiste, kes just hiljaaegu on saanud võimule tema kodumaal Itaalias. Lõppude lõpuks - ja need sõnad tuleks raiuda marmorisse kõigil linnaväljakutel - on parem olla siga kui fašist."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"Porko Rosso","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Lidotājs Porko Rosso ir Pirmā pasaules kara veterāns, kurš pārdzīvojis zināmu eksistenciālu krīzi, kuras rezultātā notikusi gan iekšēja, gan ārēja pārvērtība. Tikmēr debesīs virs Adrijas valda nemiers - gaisa pirāti terorizē apkārtni. Porko nodarbojas ar gaisa pirātu medībām, kuri aplaupa kuģus un jahtas, taču kādu dienu par mērķi kļūst viņš pats. Vai viņam izdosies izvairīties no vajāšanas un atgūt cilvēka veidolu?"},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6437c67a37b3a900949d528f","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6437c67a37b3a900949d528f","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2023-04-13T09:08:10.941Z","updated_at":"2023-04-13T09:08:11.009Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":149870,"adult":false,"title":"The Wind Rises","video":false,"overview":"A lifelong love of flight inspires Japanese aviation engineer Jiro Horikoshi, whose storied career includes the creation of the A-6M World War II fighter plane.","genre_ids":[18,16,10749,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5343,"vote_count":3289,"poster_path":"/jfwSexzlIzaOgxP9A8bTA6t8YYb.jpg","release_date":"2013-07-20","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/938lqhAQaO3hmLg44VbUR7OqlMs.jpg","original_title":"風立ちぬ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16859,"adult":false,"title":"Kiki's Delivery Service","video":false,"overview":"A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.6606,"vote_count":4461,"poster_path":"/Aufa4YdZIv4AXpR9rznwVA5SEfd.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-29","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/h5pAEVma835u8xoE60kmLVopLct.jpg","original_title":"魔女の宅急便","original_language":"ja"},{"id":21057,"adult":false,"title":"Ocean Waves","video":false,"overview":"At Kichijōji Station, Tokyo, Taku Morisaki glimpses a familiar woman on the platform opposite boarding a train. Later, her photo falls from a shelf as he exits his apartment before flying to Kōchi Prefecture. Picking it up, he looks at it briefly before leaving. As the aeroplane takes off, he narrates the events that brought her into his life...","genre_ids":[16,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1583,"vote_count":951,"poster_path":"/fSR1LLMIJZ6WcQEkM82yKy4F9vQ.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-09","vote_average":6.42,"backdrop_path":"/6ryHAHtpcNTExUVekeaNe0xmDbb.jpg","original_title":"海がきこえる","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15371,"adult":false,"title":"The Castle of Cagliostro","video":false,"overview":"After a successful robbery leaves famed thief Lupin the Third and his partner Jigen with nothing but a large amount of expertly crafted counterfeit bills, he decides to track down the forgers responsible—and steal any other treasures he may find in the Castle of Cagliostro, including the 'damsel in distress' he finds imprisoned there.","genre_ids":[16,12,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5585,"vote_count":1113,"poster_path":"/hSFdyWptoDHuXlFZGzIrfVell4Q.jpg","release_date":"1979-07-06","vote_average":7.515,"backdrop_path":"/fCf8WfsRJEDFf1N6gA6o4ICRYp.jpg","original_title":"ルパン三世 カリオストロの城","original_language":"ja"},{"id":128,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Mononoke","video":false,"overview":"Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.","genre_ids":[12,14,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.5812,"vote_count":8781,"poster_path":"/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-12","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/gl0jzn4BupSbL2qMVeqrjKkF9Js.jpg","original_title":"もののけ姫","original_language":"ja"},{"id":37797,"adult":false,"title":"Whisper of the Heart","video":false,"overview":"Shizuku lives a simple life, dominated by her love for stories and writing. One day she notices that all the library books she has have been previously checked out by the same person: 'Seiji Amasawa'.","genre_ids":[16,18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5571,"vote_count":2221,"poster_path":"/5FROLD8zpWFs9ja7aYho1uOMJHg.jpg","release_date":"1995-07-15","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/rphor0XQcYO4CQoQ6auaQm3UPap.jpg","original_title":"耳をすませば","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15283,"adult":false,"title":"Pom Poko","video":false,"overview":"The Raccoons of the Tama Hills are being forced from their homes by the rapid development of houses and shopping malls. As it becomes harder to find food and shelter, they decide to band together and fight back. The Raccoons practice and perfect the ancient art of transformation until they are even able to appear as humans in hilarious circumstances.","genre_ids":[12,16,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0533,"vote_count":1162,"poster_path":"/zat2MMhejQyJJN6CucLI9Or9kdo.jpg","release_date":"1994-07-16","vote_average":7.165,"backdrop_path":"/AouRp7KcIOVmsSuZlTXKqT4aYT2.jpg","original_title":"平成狸合戦ぽんぽこ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15370,"adult":false,"title":"The Cat Returns","video":false,"overview":"Young Haru rescues a cat from being run over, but soon learns it's no ordinary feline; it happens to be the Prince of the Cats.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.1711,"vote_count":2401,"poster_path":"/pqyY7IEWkCWNZ7EuRStQaJITEta.jpg","release_date":"2002-07-19","vote_average":7.132,"backdrop_path":"/tlQtvjwwTAAbNbtZ7IIGPlY50Hx.jpg","original_title":"猫の恩返し","original_language":"ja"},{"id":15080,"adult":false,"title":"Only Yesterday","video":false,"overview":"In lyrical switches between the present and the past, Taeko contemplates the arc of her life, and wonders if she has been true to the dreams of her childhood self.","genre_ids":[16,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2271,"vote_count":1213,"poster_path":"/tOSnFE9e82iH3ZAzSTtuOkBsabJ.jpg","release_date":"1991-07-20","vote_average":7.381,"backdrop_path":"/miA2ALg3DXiTs8BITDskYUvXcCj.jpg","original_title":"おもひでぽろぽろ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":81,"adult":false,"title":"Nausicaä of the Valley of the Wind","video":false,"overview":"After a global war, the seaside kingdom known as the Valley of the Wind remains one of the last strongholds on Earth untouched by a poisonous jungle and the powerful insects that guard it. Led by the courageous Princess Nausicaä, the people of the Valley engage in an epic struggle to restore the bond between humanity and Earth.","genre_ids":[12,16,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3279,"vote_count":3979,"poster_path":"/tcrkfB8SRPQCgwI88hQScua6nxh.jpg","release_date":"1984-03-11","vote_average":7.946,"backdrop_path":"/ulVUa2MvnJAjAeRt7h23FFJVRKH.jpg","original_title":"風の谷のナウシカ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12429,"adult":false,"title":"Ponyo","video":false,"overview":"When Sosuke, a young boy who lives on a clifftop overlooking the sea, rescues a stranded goldfish named Ponyo, he discovers more than he bargained for. Ponyo is a curious, energetic young creature who yearns to be human, but even as she causes chaos around the house, her father, a powerful sorcerer, schemes to return Ponyo to the sea.","genre_ids":[16,14,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4369,"vote_count":4710,"poster_path":"/yp8vEZflGynlEylxEesbYasc06i.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-19","vote_average":7.757,"backdrop_path":"/shqLeIkqPAAXM8iT6wVDiXUYz1p.jpg","original_title":"崖の上のポニョ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10515,"adult":false,"title":"Castle in the Sky","video":false,"overview":"A young boy and a girl with a magic crystal must race against pirates and foreign agents in a search for a legendary floating castle.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,28,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6312,"vote_count":4582,"poster_path":"/41XxSsJc5OrulP0m7TrrUeO2hoz.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-02","vote_average":7.971,"backdrop_path":"/j2ZvLJyz163MlmBFsoaDYOwxgws.jpg","original_title":"天空の城ラピュタ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8392,"adult":false,"title":"My Neighbor Totoro","video":false,"overview":"Two sisters move to the country with their father in order to be closer to their hospitalized mother, and discover the surrounding trees are inhabited by Totoros, magical spirits of the forest. When the youngest runs away from home, the older sister seeks help from the spirits to find her.","genre_ids":[14,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.3287,"vote_count":8633,"poster_path":"/rtGDOeG9LzoerkDGZF9dnVeLppL.jpg","release_date":"1988-04-16","vote_average":8.062,"backdrop_path":"/6O1mOoTXuc1WqjKd2R7MFQHZ7Eb.jpg","original_title":"となりのトトロ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":83389,"adult":false,"title":"From Up on Poppy Hill","video":false,"overview":"Yokohama, 1963. Japan is picking itself up from the devastation of World War II and preparing to host the 1964 Olympics—and the mood is one of both optimism and conflict as the young generation struggles to throw off the shackles of a troubled past. Against this backdrop of hope and change, a friendship begins to blossom between high school students Umi and Shun—but a buried secret from their past emerges to cast a shadow on the future and pull them apart.","genre_ids":[16,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1125,"vote_count":1905,"poster_path":"/rRLYX4RZIyloHSJwvZKAhphAjiB.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-16","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/v3bVN8SjeA9O0nUBtMfRcE0fJpR.jpg","original_title":"コクリコ坂から","original_language":"ja"},{"id":4935,"adult":false,"title":"Howl's Moving Castle","video":false,"overview":"Sophie, a young milliner, is turned into an elderly woman by a witch who enters her shop and curses her. She encounters a wizard named Howl and gets caught up in his resistance to fighting for the king.","genre_ids":[14,16,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.0757,"vote_count":10837,"poster_path":"/13kOl2v0nD2OLbVSHnHk8GUFEhO.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-09","vote_average":8.387,"backdrop_path":"/pjy0T63vIFYvxRSJ3ZtjB4tmWV4.jpg","original_title":"ハウルの動く城","original_language":"ja"},{"id":569950,"adult":false,"title":"It's All About Love","video":false,"overview":"The story revolve around five couples of different generations. Their lives are woven together by coincidences but sometimes through very deliberate choices where the common driving force is the search for love.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1989,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/8lxIQ2cR55Gkj2c3pys2abFnlEW.jpg","release_date":"2018-12-21","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/7tJECTGFrgwn5Dqzd3A6hyPWpHG.jpg","original_title":"Lyckligare kan ingen vara","original_language":"sv"},{"id":51739,"adult":false,"title":"The Secret World of Arrietty","video":false,"overview":"14-year-old Arrietty and the rest of the Clock family live in peaceful anonymity as they make their own home from items \"borrowed\" from the house's human inhabitants. However, life changes for the Clocks when a human boy discovers Arrietty.","genre_ids":[14,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.5226,"vote_count":3089,"poster_path":"/3lSRaSjDp2nkXMQkzzjpRi3035O.jpg","release_date":"2010-07-16","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/7Z7WVzJsSReG8B0CaPk0bvWD7tK.jpg","original_title":"借りぐらしのアリエッティ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12477,"adult":false,"title":"Grave of the Fireflies","video":false,"overview":"In the final months of World War II, 14-year-old Seita and his sister Setsuko are orphaned when their mother is killed during an air raid in Kobe, Japan. After a falling out with their aunt, they move into an abandoned bomb shelter. With no surviving relatives and their emergency rations depleted, Seita and Setsuko struggle to survive.","genre_ids":[16,18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0083,"vote_count":6367,"poster_path":"/k9tv1rXZbOhH7eiCk378x61kNQ1.jpg","release_date":"1988-04-16","vote_average":8.443,"backdrop_path":"/aHaqZpOL7UyVu0nKqp3SMz0o2E1.jpg","original_title":"火垂るの墓","original_language":"ja"},{"id":129,"adult":false,"title":"Spirited Away","video":false,"overview":"A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":21.2557,"vote_count":17989,"poster_path":"/39wmItIWsg5sZMyRUHLkWBcuVCM.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-20","vote_average":8.533,"backdrop_path":"/ukfI9QkU1aIhOhKXYWE9n3z1mFR.jpg","original_title":"千と千尋の神隠し","original_language":"ja"},{"id":5071,"adult":false,"title":"The Crazy Stranger","video":false,"overview":"A man is looking for a singer he had heard on cassette. He finds much more.","genre_ids":[18,10402,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4105,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/eM8RuoymwDaMRhR33wWTR1wXijf.jpg","release_date":"1998-04-08","vote_average":7.432,"backdrop_path":"/14KWvA1ZAiEEQyLVux5uKFxqtMV.jpg","original_title":"Gadjo Dilo","original_language":"fr"}],"similar_content":[{"id":8388,"adult":false,"title":"¡Three Amigos!","video":false,"overview":"A trio of unemployed silent film actors are mistaken for real heroes by a small Mexican village in search of someone to stop a malevolent bandit.","genre_ids":[35,37,18],"popularity":2.7558,"vote_count":1108,"poster_path":"/keQ4ra50w1nktSPRPauxpLaAM2F.jpg","release_date":"1986-12-12","vote_average":6.328,"backdrop_path":"/yMlk79kLF4GrqqP1OY0KccYB787.jpg","original_title":"¡Three Amigos!","original_language":"en"},{"id":8392,"adult":false,"title":"My Neighbor Totoro","video":false,"overview":"Two sisters move to the country with their father in order to be closer to their hospitalized mother, and discover the surrounding trees are inhabited by Totoros, magical spirits of the forest. When the youngest runs away from home, the older sister seeks help from the spirits to find her.","genre_ids":[14,16,10751],"popularity":9.3287,"vote_count":8633,"poster_path":"/rtGDOeG9LzoerkDGZF9dnVeLppL.jpg","release_date":"1988-04-16","vote_average":8.062,"backdrop_path":"/6O1mOoTXuc1WqjKd2R7MFQHZ7Eb.jpg","original_title":"となりのトトロ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1259219,"adult":false,"title":"Practice Space","video":false,"overview":"Close friends Edwin and Steven advise each other on dating and drama — based on zero experience — while seeking a space to hang after school.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.9556,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/q484KHCDvzecWdsavlURgi0hfVL.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-02","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/3N2hYV1OqO58DkJUSk28E3kcJXr.jpg","original_title":"Practice Space","original_language":"en"},{"id":8434,"adult":false,"title":"Summer Things","video":false,"overview":"Two couple of friends, one very rich, the other almost homeless, decide to go on Holiday. Julie, a single mother, joins them too. Once at seaside, it starts a complicate love cross among them that will involve also a transsexual, a jealous brother, a Latin Lover and another nervous stressed couple. Not to mention about the daughter of one of them that is secretly in Chicago with one of her father's employees... At the end of the summer, all of them will join the same party...","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.5262,"vote_count":102,"poster_path":"/laV4Xo5O1COZefAFPJLFZ28pkYS.jpg","release_date":"2002-03-04","vote_average":5.809,"backdrop_path":"/azkp4brPsmzJiyKw5ExkPDrVpWA.jpg","original_title":"Embrassez qui vous voudrez","original_language":"fr"},{"id":861101,"adult":false,"title":"Pluft, o Fantasminha","video":false,"overview":"A little kid-ghost called Pluft lives with his ghost-mother and ghost-uncle, in a remote house in a desert island. He doesn't even believe people real exist. His world will be thrown upside down, when an evil pirate (Perna de Pau) disembark on the island, after kidnapping the little girl Maribel (daughter of a famous captain), in search of Captain's hidden treasure. Three friendly sailors will help to free the girl. Based on a very well known Brazilian children's play.","genre_ids":[35,10751,14],"popularity":0.2503,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/iCrD6A21Wmzzm1v2bOVdqD8HxRP.jpg","release_date":"2022-07-21","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/4aErColaMWJruY2wer2SsXNDdPC.jpg","original_title":"Pluft, o Fantasminha","original_language":"pt"},{"id":8587,"adult":false,"title":"The Lion King","video":false,"overview":"Young lion prince Simba, eager to one day become king of the Pride Lands, grows up under the watchful eye of his father Mufasa; all the while his villainous uncle Scar conspires to take the throne for himself. Amid betrayal and tragedy, Simba must confront his past and find his rightful place in the Circle of Life.","genre_ids":[10751,16,18,12],"popularity":18.8917,"vote_count":19405,"poster_path":"/sKCr78MXSLixwmZ8DyJLrpMsd15.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-15","vote_average":8.252,"backdrop_path":"/6GF9uJs7AnbcJvyfoZyjZv063Oo.jpg","original_title":"The Lion King","original_language":"en"},{"id":471689,"adult":false,"title":"Everything Is Free","video":false,"overview":"Ivan is a US painter residing in Colombia. His best friend, Christian, and younger brother, Cole, come to visit. Somewhere along the way, Ivan and Cole hit it off although Cole is not gay. Will older brother Christian be okay with that?","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.5461,"vote_count":26,"poster_path":"/u1GV3ULs7i4LnetwweOxesXkfaK.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-03","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/nyi66GPJnN1Q93iOzwmk5oftPze.jpg","original_title":"Everything Is Free","original_language":"en"},{"id":8868,"adult":false,"title":"Asterix vs. Caesar","video":false,"overview":"Obelix falls for a new arrival in his home village in Gaul, but is heartbroken when her true love arrives to visit her. However, the lovers are kidnapped by Romans; Asterix and Obelix set out to rescue them on a dangerous journey that will involve gladiators, slavers and beauracracy - and a personal encounter with the Emperor himself, Julius Caesar...","genre_ids":[35,16,10751,12],"popularity":0.8604,"vote_count":630,"poster_path":"/8LlqOgKKU0BeZzEo1PMMIjtLuj4.jpg","release_date":"1985-03-06","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/hHAiFCrYKt2gcoXyjzx834urZpp.jpg","original_title":"Astérix et la Surprise de César","original_language":"fr"},{"id":8872,"adult":false,"title":"Wayne's World","video":false,"overview":"The adventures of two amiably aimless metal-head friends, Wayne and Garth. From Wayne's basement, the pair broadcast a talk-show called \"Wayne's World\" on local public access television. The show comes to the attention of a sleazy network executive who wants to produce a big-budget version of \"Wayne's World\"—and he also wants Wayne's girlfriend, a rock singer named Cassandra. Wayne and Garth have to battle the executive not only to save their show, but also Cassandra.","genre_ids":[35,10402],"popularity":3.0693,"vote_count":2420,"poster_path":"/fHwZnFNWR7PaS9t5EBwTvGPeoYQ.jpg","release_date":"1992-02-14","vote_average":6.691,"backdrop_path":"/lAvf5zzyOgTZmpRBRJFa7IVVqCK.jpg","original_title":"Wayne's World","original_language":"en"},{"id":8764,"adult":false,"title":"Top Secret!","video":false,"overview":"Popular and dashing American singer Nick Rivers travels to East Germany to perform in a music festival. When he loses his heart to the gorgeous Hillary Flammond, he finds himself caught up in an underground resistance movement. Rivers joins forces with Agent Cedric and Flammond to attempt the rescue of her father, Dr. Paul, from the Germans, who have captured the scientist in hopes of coercing him into building a new naval mine.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":2.8108,"vote_count":1351,"poster_path":"/hRTbfR27xghnVMs3ZJ3EhK3zzud.jpg","release_date":"1984-06-22","vote_average":7.086,"backdrop_path":"/yI0xd7X8UktQ6cb8TdWKNTOWxhm.jpg","original_title":"Top Secret!","original_language":"en"},{"id":8457,"adult":false,"title":"Drillbit Taylor","video":false,"overview":"Dealing with a sociopathic school bully, three high school freshmen hire a low-budget bodyguard to protect them, not realizing he is just a homeless beggar and petty thief looking for some easy cash.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":2.2868,"vote_count":1082,"poster_path":"/shqO696kFnM8Z4ODa3JglcjP97u.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-04","vote_average":5.822,"backdrop_path":"/yd750mff5FTjwMenmBMWRezbuSe.jpg","original_title":"Drillbit Taylor","original_language":"en"},{"id":277653,"adult":false,"title":"My Mother's Future Husband","video":false,"overview":"Headly, a 15-year-old teenager, thinks her mother, Rene, has mourned her father's death long enough, so she decides to find her a new husband by the end of the summer.","genre_ids":[10751,10749,35,10770],"popularity":0.2975,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/8zq7w5tHu9GrOZ17QncqhK3543S.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-11","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/8783nYYpFtJiPo508LsOcAD2s53.jpg","original_title":"My Mother's Future Husband","original_language":"en"},{"id":8491,"adult":false,"title":"Weekend at Bernie's","video":false,"overview":"Two young insurance corporation employees try to pretend that their murdered employer is alive by puppeteering his dead body, leading a hitman to attempt to track him down to finish him off.","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":1.9404,"vote_count":1104,"poster_path":"/4RtjBkBSqHG46uieHgTtM7oKlpo.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-05","vote_average":6.399,"backdrop_path":"/xbGROemZqyVYrIlMOHKqmV2qmG0.jpg","original_title":"Weekend at Bernie's","original_language":"en"},{"id":8545,"adult":false,"title":"Little Voice","video":false,"overview":"After the death of her father, Little Voice or LV becomes a virtual recluse, never going out and hardly ever saying a word. She just sits in her bedroom listening to her father's collection of old records of Shirley Bassey, Marilyn Monroe and various other famous female singers. But at night time, LV sings, imitating these great singers with surprising accuracy. One night she is overheard by one of her mother's boyfriends, who happens to be a talent agent. He manages to convince her that her talent is special and arranges for her to perform at the local night club, but several problems arise.","genre_ids":[35,18,10402],"popularity":0.9335,"vote_count":196,"poster_path":"/7VxdMxSa3BEAvGl5nLvsgpBwrZH.jpg","release_date":"1998-11-05","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/lwluU3TYXBL4AllSxhgqRlhGEIY.jpg","original_title":"Little Voice","original_language":"en"},{"id":8776,"adult":false,"title":"The Toth Family","video":false,"overview":"The Toth family resides in Northern Hungary. The couple has a daughter and a son, the latter a member of the armed forces. When his weary major is ordered to take a vacation, the son talks him into a visit to his family home. Comedy ensues when the Toths go overboard trying to make things pleasant for the visiting major in hopes of an easier life for their son the soldier.","genre_ids":[18,10752,35],"popularity":1.5991,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/oSjxEkgwITSdpi7lIIIpxZ546g9.jpg","release_date":"1969-11-29","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/wUeNS3fsxtDzGnCJizGnd4vu1lV.jpg","original_title":"Isten hozta, őrnagy úr!","original_language":"hu"},{"id":9890,"adult":false,"title":"The Stepford Wives","video":false,"overview":"What does it take to become a Stepford wife, a woman perfect beyond belief? Ask the Stepford husbands, who've created this high-tech, terrifying little town.","genre_ids":[35,878,27],"popularity":2.4277,"vote_count":1396,"poster_path":"/ygr0Wlmm1KmE16TUefNitIscVBG.jpg","release_date":"2004-06-10","vote_average":5.683,"backdrop_path":"/rjUeBEhX3xZ5gN5RNcCwUDGHCqx.jpg","original_title":"The Stepford Wives","original_language":"en"},{"id":9892,"adult":false,"title":"Stranger Than Fiction","video":false,"overview":"Nothing is as it seems when four friends agree to cover up a killing. When they begin to doubt who among them is telling the truth, they find that life can be stranger than fiction.","genre_ids":[35,53],"popularity":0.3174,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/3d54NNXZnpIq7H9UyITVbM8yEiw.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-16","vote_average":5.619,"backdrop_path":"/tOnKQ7VLfyfnB5LGB1Lp4JPPFHD.jpg","original_title":"Stranger Than Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":9929,"adult":false,"title":"Asterix and Cleopatra","video":false,"overview":"Popular animated hero Asterix and his faithful sidekick Obelix travel to ancient Egypt to help Cleopatra build a new summer home. Cleopatra and Julius Caesar have made a bet, with Caesar wagering the project cannot be completed in a few weeks time. With the help of a magic potion, Asterix comes to the rescue of the Queen of the Nile as Caesar and an angry architect plot against them.","genre_ids":[10751,16,12,35],"popularity":1.1984,"vote_count":1010,"poster_path":"/gNpKAmWFsCiWKKx39Ap8pF7EWQg.jpg","release_date":"1968-12-19","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/ort14Ott2BvpfmTuhsMUVnSEsWd.jpg","original_title":"Astérix et Cléopâtre","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1260922,"adult":false,"title":"Found Footage: The Making of the Patterson Project","video":false,"overview":"A crew of acclaimed documentarians follow a young budding filmmaker as he attempts to create the world's greatest found footage horror film.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":0.2816,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/jrUgZbo6OAuGXGywuvx7Tl0dWm4.jpg","release_date":"2025-0